  The error also appears after the shell is launched with [`zsh --emulate sh`](https://www.zsh.org/mla/workers/2021/msg00072.html). This suggests that something else in `~/.zshrc` is [setting options](https://unix.stackexchange.com/a/663726) that are causing the issue, possibly due to an interaction with [`oh-my-zsh`](https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/issues/10611). You may need to rebuild`~/.zshrc` one piece at a time to find the problem.
  
  
  
