  ## Solved
  
  The issue was this line in my .zprofile which I thought I had to add after installing [posh-git-sh](https://github.com/lyze/posh-git-sh) (step 3) `[[ -e ~/.zshrc ]] && emulate sh -c 'source ~/.zshrc'`
  
  Once I removed it the expected behaviour returned
  
